file browser structure:
faves
- folder
-- open
-- remove from bookmarks
- folder
-- open
-- remove from bookmarks
+---+
- mounted drive
-- open
-- unmount
folder
- ops
-- copy to > folders
-- cut to > folders
-- rename
-- open
-- delete
-- move to trash
-- information
- file
-- copy to > folders
-- cut to > folders
-- rename
-- open
-- delete
-- move to trash
-- information
file
- copy to > folders
- cut to > folders
- rename
- open
- delete
- move to trash
- information
file
file

